# HEX ONLY (read-safe). display-deception canary: U+202E (RLO) + the REVERSED canary
# token, so a bidi-rendering terminal DISPLAYS 'POC-CORPUS-CANARY-FIRED' while the
# logical bytes are scrambled. A neutralizing terminal shows the scrambled form.
e2 80 ae 44 45 52 49 46 2d 59 52 41 4e 41 43 2d 53 55 50 52 4f 43 2d 43 4f 50
